Natalie Cassidy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natalie_Cassidy 0 Natalie Ann Cassidy (born 13 May 1983) is a two time British Soap Award-winning English actress. She has played Sonia Fowler in EastEnders since 1993, appeared in the BBC Two sitcom-horror Psychoville and was a contestant on the seventh series of Strictly Come Dancing and the ninth series of Celebrity Big Brother.
